# PhotogrammetrySession.Configuration.FeatureSensitivity.normal

**Case**

The session uses the default algorithm to detect landmarks.

## Declaration

```swift
case normal
```

## Specifying feature sensitivity

- **PhotogrammetrySession.Configuration.FeatureSensitivity.high**: The session uses a slower, more sensitive algorithm to detect landmarks.
